{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'd like to start with a short story."},{"time":5000,"text":"It's about a little boy"},{"time":7000,"text":"whose father was a history buff"},{"time":12000,"text":"and who used to take him by the hand"},{"time":14000,"text":"to visit the ruins of an ancient metropolis"},{"time":18000,"text":"on the outskirts of their camp."},{"time":21000,"text":"They would always stop by to visit"},{"time":24000,"text":"these huge winged bulls that used to guard"},{"time":27000,"text":"the gates of that ancient metropolis,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and the boy used to be scared"},{"time":31000,"text":"of these winged bulls,"},{"time":33000,"text":"but at the same time they excited him."},{"time":35000,"text":"And the dad used to use those bulls"},{"time":37000,"text":"to tell the boy stories about"},{"time":39000,"text":"that civilization and their work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"Let's fast-forward to the"},{"time":46000,"text":"San Francisco Bay Area many decades later,"},{"time":49000,"text":"where I started a technology company"},{"time":52000,"text":"that brought the world its first"},{"time":55000,"text":"3D laser scanning system."},{"time":57000,"text":"Let me show you how it works."},{"time":59000,"text":"Female Voice: Long range laser scanning"},{"time":61000,"text":"by sending out a pulse that's a laser beam of light."},{"time":64000,"text":"The system measures the beam's time of flight,"},{"time":66000,"text":"recording the time it takes for the light"},{"time":68000,"text":"to hit a surface and make its return."},{"time":71000,"text":"With two mirrors, the scanner calculates"},{"time":73000,"text":"the beam's horizontal and vertical angles,"},{"time":76000,"text":"giving accurate x, y, and z coordinates."},{"time":79000,"text":"The point is then recorded"},{"time":81000,"text":"into a 3D visualization program."},{"time":86000,"text":"All of this happens in seconds."},{"time":91000,"text":"Ben Kacyra: You can see here,"},{"time":93000,"text":"these systems are extremely fast."},{"time":96000,"text":"They collect millions of points at a time"},{"time":99000,"text":"with very high accuracy"},{"time":101000,"text":"and very high resolution."},{"time":103000,"text":"A surveyor with traditional survey tools"},{"time":106000,"text":"would be hard-pressed to produce"},{"time":108000,"text":"maybe 500 points in a whole day."},{"time":111000,"text":"These babies would be producing"},{"time":114000,"text":"something like ten thousand points a second."},{"time":117000,"text":"So, as you can imagine,"},{"time":119000,"text":"this was a paradigm shift"},{"time":122000,"text":"in the survey and construction"},{"time":124000,"text":"as well as in reality capture industry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"Approximately ten years ago,"},{"time":134000,"text":"my wife and I started a foundation to do good,"},{"time":137000,"text":"and right about that time,"},{"time":139000,"text":"the magnificent Bamiyan Buddhas,"},{"time":142000,"text":"hundred and eighty foot tall in Afghanistan,"},{"time":145000,"text":"were blown up by the Taliban."},{"time":148000,"text":"They were gone in an instant."},{"time":150000,"text":"And unfortunately, there was"},{"time":152000,"text":"no detailed documentation of these Buddhas."},{"time":154000,"text":"This clearly devastated me,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and I couldn't help but wonder about"},{"time":158000,"text":"the fate of my old friends, the winged bulls,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and the fate of the many, many"},{"time":164000,"text":"heritage sites all over the world."},{"time":167000,"text":"Both my wife and I"},{"time":169000,"text":"were so touched by this"},{"time":171000,"text":"that we decided to"},{"time":173000,"text":"expand the mission of our foundation"},{"time":176000,"text":"to include digital heritage preservation"},{"time":180000,"text":"of world sites."},{"time":182000,"text":"We called the project CyArk,"},{"time":185000,"text":"which stands for Cyber Archive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187000,"text":"To date, with the help of"},{"time":189000,"text":"a global network of partners,"},{"time":192000,"text":"we've completed close to fifty projects."},{"time":194000,"text":"Let me show you some of them:"},{"time":196000,"text":"Chichen Itza,"},{"time":198000,"text":"Rapa Nui --"},{"time":200000,"text":"and what you're seeing here"},{"time":202000,"text":"are the cloud of points --"},{"time":204000,"text":"Babylon,"},{"time":206000,"text":"Rosslyn Chapel,"},{"time":208000,"text":"Pompeii,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and our latest project, Mt. Rushmore,"},{"time":212000,"text":"which happened to be one of"},{"time":214000,"text":"our most challenging projects."},{"time":216000,"text":"As you see here, we had to develop"},{"time":218000,"text":"a special rig to bring the scanner"},{"time":221000,"text":"up close and personal."},{"time":224000,"text":"The results of our work in the field"},{"time":227000,"text":"are used to produce"},{"time":229000,"text":"media and deliverables to be used"},{"time":231000,"text":"by conservators and researchers."},{"time":234000,"text":"We also produce media for"},{"time":238000,"text":"dissemination to the public --"},{"time":241000,"text":"free through the CyArk website."},{"time":244000,"text":"These would be used for education,"},{"time":247000,"text":"cultural tourism, etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"What you're looking at in here"},{"time":251000,"text":"is a 3D viewer that we developed"},{"time":254000,"text":"that would allow the display"},{"time":256000,"text":"and manipulation of [the] cloud of points"},{"time":258000,"text":"in real time, cutting sections through them"},{"time":261000,"text":"and extracting dimensions."},{"time":263000,"text":"This happens to be the cloud of points"},{"time":265000,"text":"for Tikal."},{"time":266000,"text":"In here you see a traditional 2D"},{"time":268000,"text":"architectural engineering drawing"},{"time":270000,"text":"that's used for preservation, and of course"},{"time":273000,"text":"we tell the stories through fly-throughs."},{"time":276000,"text":"And here, this is a fly-through"},{"time":278000,"text":"the cloud of points of Tikal,"},{"time":280000,"text":"and here you see it rendered"},{"time":283000,"text":"and photo-textured with the photography"},{"time":285000,"text":"that we take of the site."},{"time":288000,"text":"And so this is not a video."},{"time":290000,"text":"This is actual 3D points with"},{"time":292000,"text":"two to three millimeter accuracy."},{"time":296000,"text":"And of course the data can be used"},{"time":298000,"text":"to develop 3D models that are"},{"time":301000,"text":"very accurate and very detailed."},{"time":304000,"text":"And here you're looking at a model"},{"time":306000,"text":"that's extracted from the cloud of points"},{"time":308000,"text":"for Stirling Castle."},{"time":310000,"text":"It's used for studies, for visualization,"},{"time":313000,"text":"as well as for education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316000,"text":"And finally, we produce mobile apps"},{"time":318000,"text":"that include narrated virtual tools."},{"time":322000,"text":"The more I got involved"},{"time":325000,"text":"in the heritage field,"},{"time":327000,"text":"the more it became clear to me"},{"time":330000,"text":"that we are losing the sites"},{"time":333000,"text":"and the stories faster than we can"},{"time":336000,"text":"physically preserve them."},{"time":339000,"text":"Of course, earthquakes"},{"time":341000,"text":"and all the natural phenomena --"},{"time":343000,"text":"floods, tornadoes, etc. --"},{"time":345000,"text":"take their toll."},{"time":348000,"text":"However, what occurred to me was"},{"time":351000,"text":"human-caused destruction, which was"},{"time":353000,"text":"not only causing a significant portion"},{"time":355000,"text":"of the destruction, but actually"},{"time":358000,"text":"it was accelerating."},{"time":361000,"text":"This includes arson,"},{"time":363000,"text":"urban sprawl,"},{"time":365000,"text":"acid rain, not to mention"},{"time":368000,"text":"terrorism and wars."},{"time":370000,"text":"It was getting more and more apparent"},{"time":373000,"text":"that we're fighting a losing battle."},{"time":375000,"text":"We're losing our sites"},{"time":377000,"text":"and the stories,"},{"time":379000,"text":"and basically we're losing"},{"time":381000,"text":"a piece -- and a significant piece --"},{"time":383000,"text":"of our collective memory."},{"time":386000,"text":"Imagine us as a human race"},{"time":388000,"text":"not knowing where we came from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392000,"text":"Luckily, in the last two or three decades,"},{"time":395000,"text":"digital technologies have been developing"},{"time":398000,"text":"that have helped us to develop tools"},{"time":400000,"text":"that we've brought to bear"},{"time":402000,"text":"in the digital preservation,"},{"time":404000,"text":"in our digital preservation war."},{"time":406000,"text":"This includes, for example,"},{"time":408000,"text":"the 3D laser scanning systems,"},{"time":412000,"text":"ever more powerful personal computers,"},{"time":415000,"text":"3D graphics,"},{"time":417000,"text":"high-definition digital photography,"},{"time":420000,"text":"not to mention the Internet."},{"time":423000,"text":"Because of this accelerated"},{"time":425000,"text":"pace of destruction,"},{"time":427000,"text":"it became clear to us that we needed"},{"time":429000,"text":"to challenge ourselves and our partners"},{"time":432000,"text":"to accelerate our work."},{"time":434000,"text":"And we created a project"},{"time":436000,"text":"we call the CyArk 500 Challenge --"},{"time":439000,"text":"and that is to digitally preserve"},{"time":442000,"text":"500 World Heritage Sites"},{"time":445000,"text":"in five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"We do have the technology"},{"time":449000,"text":"that's scaleable,"},{"time":451000,"text":"and our network of global partners"},{"time":455000,"text":"has been expanding and can be expanded"},{"time":458000,"text":"at a rapid rate,"},{"time":460000,"text":"so we're comfortable"},{"time":462000,"text":"that this task can be accomplished."},{"time":465000,"text":"However, to me, the 500 is"},{"time":468000,"text":"really just the first 500."},{"time":472000,"text":"In order to sustain our work into the future,"},{"time":476000,"text":"we use technology centers"},{"time":479000,"text":"where we partner with"},{"time":482000,"text":"local universities and colleges"},{"time":484000,"text":"to take the technology to them,"},{"time":487000,"text":"whereby they then can help us"},{"time":490000,"text":"with digital preservation of their heritage sites,"},{"time":493000,"text":"and at the same time, it gives them"},{"time":496000,"text":"the technology to benefit from in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500000,"text":"Let me close with another short story."},{"time":504000,"text":"Two years ago, we were approached"},{"time":506000,"text":"by a partner of ours to digitally preserve"},{"time":509000,"text":"an important heritage site,"},{"time":511000,"text":"a UNESCO heritage site in Uganda,"},{"time":514000,"text":"the Royal Kasubi Tombs."},{"time":517000,"text":"The work was done successfully in the field,"},{"time":520000,"text":"and the data was archived"},{"time":522000,"text":"and publicly disseminated"},{"time":524000,"text":"through the CyArk website."},{"time":527000,"text":"Last March,"},{"time":529000,"text":"we received very sad news."},{"time":532000,"text":"The Royal Tombs had been destroyed"},{"time":535000,"text":"by suspected arson."},{"time":538000,"text":"A few days later, we received a call:"},{"time":541000,"text":"\"Is the data available"},{"time":544000,"text":"and can it be used for reconstruction?\""},{"time":548000,"text":"Our answer, of course, was yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"Let me leave you with a final thought."},{"time":556000,"text":"Our heritage is much more than"},{"time":559000,"text":"our collective memory --"},{"time":561000,"text":"it's our collective treasure."},{"time":563000,"text":"We owe it to our children,"},{"time":566000,"text":"our grandchildren and the generations"},{"time":568000,"text":"we will never meet"},{"time":571000,"text":"to keep it safe"},{"time":573000,"text":"and to pass it along."},{"time":575000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":579000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"Well, I'm staying here because"},{"time":598000,"text":"we wanted to demonstrate to you"},{"time":601000,"text":"the power of this technology"},{"time":604000,"text":"and so, while I've been speaking,"},{"time":607000,"text":"you have been scanned."},{"time":610000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":614000,"text":"The two wizards that I have"},{"time":617000,"text":"that are behind the curtain"},{"time":619000,"text":"will help me bring"},{"time":622000,"text":"the results on the screen."},{"time":630000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"This is all in 3D and of course"},{"time":640000,"text":"you can fly through the cloud of points."},{"time":643000,"text":"You can look at it from on top,"},{"time":645000,"text":"from the ceiling."},{"time":647000,"text":"You can look from different vantage points,"},{"time":649000,"text":"but I'm going to ask Doug to zoom in"},{"time":652000,"text":"on an individual in the crowd,"},{"time":655000,"text":"just to show the amount of detail"},{"time":658000,"text":"that we can create."},{"time":664000,"text":"So you have been digitally preserved"},{"time":667000,"text":"in about four minutes."},{"time":669000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671000,"text":"I'd like to thank the wizards here."},{"time":675000,"text":"We were very lucky to have"},{"time":678000,"text":"two of our partners participate in this:"},{"time":682000,"text":"the Historic Scotland,"},{"time":684000,"text":"and the Glasgow School of Art."},{"time":687000,"text":"I'd like to also thank personally"},{"time":691000,"text":"the efforts of David Mitchell,"},{"time":695000,"text":"who is the Director of Conservation"},{"time":698000,"text":"at Historic Scotland."},{"time":700000,"text":"David."},{"time":702000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":707000,"text":"And Doug Pritchard, who's the Head of"},{"time":709000,"text":"Visualization at the Glasgow School of Art."},{"time":712000,"text":"Let's give them a hand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":717000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}